  "keyFeatures": [
    "Astro-based static site with optimized performance",
    "Content collections for blog, portfolio works, books, and talks",
    "MDX support for rich content authoring",
    "RSS feed aggregation from external platforms (Zenn, Note, Podcast)",
    "Automatic OG image generation with Satori",
    "Reading time calculation for blog posts",
    "Full-text search with Pagefind integration",
    "Responsive UI components built with Tailwind CSS",
    "SEO optimized with sitemap and RSS feed generation",
    "ENS (Ethereum Name Service) integration",
    "Cloudflare Pages deployment with Wrangler",
